description: Number of partitions of n into 5 distinct nonzero squares.
maple: From _R. J. Mathar_, Oct 18 2010: (Start)A025444aux := proc(n,m,nmax) local a,m,upn,lv ; if m = 1 then if issqr(n) and nmax^2 >= n and n >= 1 then return 1; else return 0; end if; else a := 0 ; for upn from 1 to nmax do lv := n-upn^2 ; if lv <0 then break; end if; a := a + procname(lv,m-1,upn-1) ; end do: return a; end if; end proc:A025444 := proc(n) A025444aux(n,5,n) ; end proc: (End)
author: _David W. Wilson_
